Every new parent has been jolted out of bed in the middle of the night by the cries of their baby. As you get to your baby’s room
column13: half asleep and jostled by your baby\u2019s sharp crying
column14:
you find it almost impossible to locate your little one\u2019s pacifier. Farlin understands how parents can find these midnight tussles absolutely stressful and has created a very practical pacifier that can make life so much simpler. The Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in the Dark pacifier glows in the dark and allows you to find the pacifier in the jiffy and calm your baby in no time. The pacifier renders orthodontic advantages as well.

\r\n

\r\n\tMade from high quality silicone this firm and flexible pacifier promotes the natural development of your baby\u2019s palate
column15:
teeth and gums. The pacifier is soft and easy to suck and reduces pressure on the jaw during sucking. The bulb of the teat is designed to allow proper tongue placement during sucking. The glow-in-the-dark pacifier from Farlin is suitable for babies aged 6 to 8 months. The pacifier is durable and maintains its shape even after long use. The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. Now you can enjoy peace and quiet while you put your baby to bed or prepare their bottle and your baby enjoys soothing comfort with the Farlin Orthodontic pacifier.
